# About Section

## Layout
Two column grid on desktop, single column on mobile.
Left column: 30% width. Right column: 65% width.
Gap between columns: gap-16 lg:gap-24.
Section padding: px-6 md:px-16 lg:px-24 py-24 md:py-32.

## Background
bg-[var(--bg-primary)] — same as hero.
Top border: border-t border-[var(--custom-border)].

## Section id
id="about"

## Left Column
- Section label: "01 — ABOUT"
  font-display, text-xs, uppercase, tracking-widest,
  text-[var(--text-muted)], mb-8
- Name: "Sam Dhanalakota"
  font-display, text-3xl md:text-4xl, font-bold,
  text-[var(--text-primary)], mt-2
- Title: "SENIOR FULL-STACK ENGINEER"
  font-display, text-xs, uppercase, tracking-widest,
  text-[var(--text-muted)], mt-2
- Secondary heading: "What I've built"
  font-display, text-xl md:text-2xl, font-bold,
  text-[var(--text-primary)], mt-16

## Right Column
- Primary paragraph:
  text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl, font-bold,
  leading-tight, text-[var(--text-primary)],
  font-display, mb-8
- Secondary paragraph:
  text-base md:text-lg, leading-relaxed,
  text-[var(--text-secondary)]

## Animations
Scroll-triggered fade-up using framer-motion.
viewport={{ once: true, margin: "-100px" }}
Left column: initial opacity 0 x -30, animate opacity 1 x 0, delay 0.1
Right column primary: initial opacity 0 y 30, animate opacity 1 y 0, delay 0.2
Right column secondary: initial opacity 0 y 20, animate opacity 1 y 0, delay 0.35

## Rules
- "use client" required
- CSS Modules for layout: About.module.css
- No inline styles
- No hardcoded colors
- All text from useTranslation('about')
- Add 'about' to Namespace type in lib/i18n/config.ts
- Import about.json in lib/i18n/config.ts